&lt;li>&lt;strong>Extended Support (2024)&lt;/strong>:
&lt;a href="https://2i2c.org/blog/2024/funding-czi/" >Support from CZI to sustain 2i2c&amp;rsquo;s mission&lt;/a> - ~$700K over one year for continued operations&lt;/li>
